== 35hp_minecraft_circle ==
Made by LolDude the 6th >>
>> loldude6th@gmail.com >>

Genre: 35hp (knife fight)
Released: 05/02/2013
CPU/GPU demanding: Very low [Default textures- 128x128, lightmap scale 16]
Requires custom textures: NO.

== Instructions ==
Install =-
1. Download and extract the "maps" folder from the archive to "steam/steamapps/YOUR_USER_NAME/counter-strike source/cstrike".

* There is a FastDL folder, for Fast Download servers, copy the .bz2 archive into your server.

Please Email me if you find any bugs.
